Class LongDistribution

    Distribution<Long>, Serializable

    public class LongDistribution
extends UpdatableDistribution<Long>

    Distribution<Long> implementation which records a distribution into a Map<Long, Place>.

        public LongDistribution()
        Default constructor.

        Creates a blank distribution which may be registered with DistIdMap.registerDistribution(UpdatableDistribution) to be updated with that collection's distribution automatically.

      • LongDistribution

        public LongDistribution(Map<Long,apgas.Place> map)
        Creates a new LongDistribution based on the given mappings from Long to Place

        A copy of the map given as parameter is created. Changes to the created LongDistribution will not be reflected into the map given as parameter and vice-versa.

        Parameters:
        map - mappings of Long indices to Place based on which to construct a new LongDistribution
